<h3 headerid="4" name="text"><a id="c2" name="c2"></a><strong>General and Basic Course Requirements</strong></h3>
<p>Students should take <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=ENGL%20160" title="ENGL 160" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ENGL 160');">ENGL 160</a></span> and <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=ENGL%20161" title="ENGL 161" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ENGL 161');">ENGL 161</a></span>, the courses of one of the mathematics tracks, and <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=ECON%20120" title="ECON 120" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ECON 120');">ECON 120</a></span> as early as possible, since this course is a prerequisite for some business core courses.</p>

