elink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 180');">MATH 180</a></span> and <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20181" title="MATH 181" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 181');">MATH 181</a></span>, or one higher-level math course (<span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20210" title="MATH 210" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 210');">MATH 210</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20220" title="MATH 220" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 220');">MATH 220</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20310" title="MATH 310" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 310');">MATH 310</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20320" title="MATH 320" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 320');">MATH 320</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20410" title="MATH 410" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 410');">MATH 410</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20411" title="MATH 411" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 411');">MATH 411</a></span>, <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=MATH%20425" title="MATH 425" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 425');">MATH 425</a></span>), will have fulfilled the math sequence.</em></p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" class="symcol">d</td><td class="notecol"><p><em>Required for students who enter the College of Business Administration as transfer students. <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=BA%20420" title="BA 420" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'BA 420');">BA 420</a></span> will be applied as credit toward the degree for all Bachelor of Science programs, reducing the hours of general electives.</em></p></t