<h4>University General Education Requirements</h4>
<p>Students must satisfy the university’s General Education requirements by taking classes from various subject areas. The requirement in some of these subject areas may be fulfilled through the required courses listed above. For the categories with additional hours, students should consult the<em> <a href="/ucat/degree-programs/general-education/">General Education</a></em> section of the catalog for a list of courses in each category.</p>
